This falls under the category of Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) and Graph Theory (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the Efficient Domination problem, which is a computational problem, and thus could fall under the category of Computational Geometry (cs.CG) or Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
